person.bio: CTO at Presearch, building a decentralized search engine powered by community. Experienced Engineering and Data Science Executive with a demonstrated history building incredibly strong software teams and products. Particularly strong background in the Search and Information Retrieval, Recommendation Systems, and Data Analytics spaces.
